Class StringUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.zachohara.bukkit.simpleplugin.util.StringUtil

  • public final class StringUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    The StringUtil class contains some common strings that are exchanged between the server and the players using it.

    Zach Ohara
